{"tid":1835358,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單講下口罩同隻病毒","createTime":"2020-01-22T23:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:54:28.000Z","uid":205098,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c80ded4adc584b51667d8d2c3e9519dd551093e1","tid":1835358,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:15:50.000Z","msg":"一日確診兩單wars，大家出街保護好自己，盡量戴返個口罩同勤洗手，如果出現上呼吸道感染徵狀就盡快去睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n一般我地接觸到既口罩會分為3種，分別係：<br />\n1.常見外科口罩 surgical mask<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VYKbiA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VYKbiA.jpg&h=f000d901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 防塵口罩 dust mask <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xakMpDH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxakMpDH.png&h=e923804b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 呼吸器 respirator mask （eg N95）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UepVLr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UepVLr.jpg&h=c6c7ad14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n首先講下第一種外科口罩。佢哋個構造通常分成三層，最出邊冇顏色嗰層可以防濺、而中間嗰層係口罩既filter可以stops到啲microbes出入 ，內層就可以吸收返你呼出既濕氣（所以有顏色要戴係出面）。唔同牌子既外科口罩效能可能唔同，要睇返個包裝（例如pm2.5係指可以block到2.5 micrometer (&mu;m)以上既particles），但根據返之前University of Massachusetts做既研究，surgical mask普遍可以capture到～60%&gt;0.3 &mu;m既particles同90%&gt;2.5 &mu;m既particles。但要留意返戴既時間，通常建議係每4小時/feel到個口罩濕咗就要換<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而dust mask 通常只能夠過濾較大既particles，所以擋唔到飛沬/細菌病毒，對預防感染係冇乜用既，唔使考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後係respirator mask。用n95做例子，佢95既意思係可以係測試中至少有效block到95% 既極細小particles (標準係0.3 &mu;m)。n95可以block到較細既粒子，但並唔代表佢好啲。事實上，我地用n95前都有經過fit test，黎確保個size可以緊密貼合塊面，冇經過fit test攞respirator黎戴，如果個size同你塊面唔夠貼合，其實效果同戴普通既surgical mask差唔多。如果唔係需要長時間暴露係高風險區域，其實冇需要戴n95<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，普通外科口罩係最好既選擇，但要正確咁戴。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n順便再講下隻濕鳩病毒，wars只係佢既花名，目前WHO應該仲係叫緊佢做2019-nCov。同sars/mers一樣，都屬冠狀病毒（Coronavirus）。virus黎講，除左小數flu/皰疹病毒係有特效藥醫外，其他都係冇既。所以我地只可以根據個patient表現出黎既symptoms黎俾藥，藉此撐過危險期，再靠自身既immune system黎消滅隻virus。而Coronavirus最大既特點就係可以同時causing illness係人同其他動物，但animal coronaviruses 造成既evolve and infect people就好少見，而sars同mers正係咁樣出現。<br />\n<br />\n目前我地對2019-nCov既了解仲係好少，但根據佢既genetic sequence可以知道佢同sars/mers十分相似。以目前感染數字上升既速度同之前sars/mers既經驗黎睇，2019-nCov 透過person-to-person黎spread幾乎係可以肯定既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n原本只係想提下大家出街要戴口罩，點知一個唔為意9up咗咁多，冇訓可能有好多typo大家將就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。總而言之，大家注意健康，正確戴口罩同勤洗手，唔好去高風險地區。<br />\n<br />\n如果篇文有錯/唔清楚既地方，歡迎各位ching幫手指正/補充。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後呼籲各位支那人摘下口罩，做個堂堂正正既中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twRckcP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwRckcP.jpg&h=614377d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"c4fa9e60e5261d0a71a37582c57e881817c15deb","tid":1835358,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6059d4a299d8751652491308a19d3f8120f713","tid":1835358,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b52871685f85086c23b200a8750287e817baf4","tid":1835358,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:23:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ada3b2d2e349514ba045236366ea9730382cab","tid":1835358,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:25:09.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"c6732a2b3b16a936dcec7da17131fb288cc120a3","tid":1835358,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:25:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下護目鏡？<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎會經眼傳播<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1835326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1835326</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大陸人：眼睛接触到也会传染<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1835347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1835347</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"635331691bd93775540ed24b2a1363fc3aef80c5","tid":1835358,"uid":85578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:25:40.000Z","msg":"有無好返既例子？<br />\n同埋死既人係多數因為個病而死，定係因為有其他大病搞到死？"},{"pid":"c72734f207de5736f766bf283858b8fec8ee3de0","tid":1835358,"uid":84968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cbd59c2e42fc81dd919011adb54ec5bc8db7a0","tid":1835358,"uid":25587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84160745feb7ae8891ad8607f5bc6e8efecf2fbe","tid":1835358,"uid":47840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo